Bradt, Respondent, v. Scott et al., Appellants. (Supreme Court, General Term, Third Department. March 15, 1892.) Action by Fred A. Bradt against James T. Scott and others.

Argued before Mayham, P. J., and Putnam and Herrick, JJ.

Ho opinion. Order opening default on payment of costs. See 18 N. Y. Supp. 507.
